#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.multi_modal.generate:1 of
msgid ""
"Generate text with multi model llm based on given data and prompt "
"template."
msgstr "基于给定的数据和提示模板，使用多模态大语言模型生成文本。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.multi_modal.generate of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.multi_modal.generate:3 of
msgid ""
"Input data used for generation. Can be maxframe DataFrame, Series that "
"contain text to be processed."
msgstr "用于生成的输入数据。可以是包含待处理文本的 maxframe DataFrame 或 Series。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.multi_modal.generate:5 of
msgid ""
"Language model instance support **MultiModal** inputs used for text "
"generation."
msgstr "支持 **MultiModal** 输入的用于文本生成的语言模型实例。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.multi_modal.generate:7 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"List of message with column names as placeholders. Each message contains "
"a role and content. Content is a list of dict, each dict contains a text "
"or image, the value can reference column data from input.  Here is an "
"example of prompt template.  .. code-block:: python      [         {"
"             \"role\": \"<role>\",  # e.g. \"user\" or \"assistant\""
"             \"content\": [                 {                     # At "
"least one of these fields is required                     \"image\": "
"\"<image_data_url>\",  # optional                     \"text\": "
"\"<prompt_text_template>\"  # optional                 },"
"                 ...             ]         }     ]  Where:  - ``text`` "
"can be a Python format string using column names from input data as "
"parameters (e.g. ``\"{column_name}\"``) - ``image`` should be a DataURL "
"string following `RFC2397 "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Data_URI_scheme>`_ standard with format.  "
".. code-block:: none      data:<mime_type>[;base64],<column_name>"
msgstr ""
"包含以列名作为占位符的消息列表。每条消息包含一个角色和内容。内容是一个"
"字典列表，每个字典包含文本或图像，值可以引用输入数据中的列。以下是一个"
"提示模板的示例。"

