#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.multi_modal.generate:47 of
msgid ""
"The ``api_key_resource`` parameter should reference a text file resource "
"in MaxCompute that contains only your DashScope API key."
msgstr ""
"``api_key_resource`` 参数应引用 MaxCompute 中仅包含 DashScope API 密钥的"
"文本文件资源。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.multi_modal.generate:49 of
msgid ""
"Using DashScope services requires enabling public network access for your"
" MaxCompute project. This can be configured through the MaxCompute "
"console by `enabling the Internet access feature "
"<https://help.aliyun.com/zh/maxcompute/user-guide/network-connection-"
"process>`_ for your project. Without this configuration, the API calls to"
" DashScope will fail due to network connectivity issues."
msgstr ""
"使用 DashScope 服务需要为您的 MaxCompute 项目启用公网访问。这可通过 "
"MaxCompute 控制台为您的项目`启用 Internet 访问功能 <https://help.aliyun."
"com/zh/maxcompute/user-guide/network-connection-process>`_ 来配置。没有此"
"配置，对 DashScope 的 API 调用将因网络连接问题而失败。"

